title: +450 SVG logos and things
description:
This is a big colletion of 450 logos and other vectorized stuff in SVG format, much of them vectorized from inskape, other are just high resolution auto vectorizers, others are Illustrator (AI) direct exportation... al made for support on MODERN web browsers (modern ones, you know what IE mean...).. i think it's fully compatible with ILLUSTRATOR, FREEHAND and other non-open source vector software.

i apologize cause there are some PNG or JPG files in the package

algo there are 2 folders with some other SVG stuff
